thread.title: Energy Transfer, Williams Said to Plan Florida Asset Sale
thread.title_full: Energy Transfer, Williams Said to Plan Florida Asset Sale - Bloomberg Business

author: Bloomberg.com
title: Energy Transfer, Williams Said to Plan Florida Asset Sale
text:
(Bloomberg) -- Energy Transfer Equity and Williams Cos. areplanning to sell WMB’s stake in one of Florida’s main interstatepipelines to win regulatory approval for $37.7b merger, peoplewith knowledge of the matter told Bloomberg.
* Co. anticipate that sale of WMB’s 50% stake in Gulfstream
Natural Gas System will be required by FTC: people said * WMB may explore selling its stake to Spectra Energy
Partners, which owns the other half: people said * ETE aims to hold onto its 50% stake in the only other major
interstate pipeline currently operating in Fla. (JV with
Kinder Morgan) * WMB, ETE declined to commentSee full story
